WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.340 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 11]

02:56.690 --> 02:57.770
Why?

02:58.620 --> 03:00.960
Why did Master do this to me?

03:01.720 --> 03:03.090
Why?

03:03.780 --> 03:05.020
Why?

03:05.810 --> 03:06.650
No.

03:06.670 --> 03:07.270
No.

03:08.840 --> 03:10.210
Ling Long is dead.

03:11.240 --> 03:12.720
The legend is fake.

03:13.860 --> 03:15.750
Ling Long didn't slaughter the Kunlun Sect.

03:16.079 --> 03:17.290
The Fox Clan didn't do it either.

03:17.310 --> 03:18.750
It was Rong Xian!

03:22.870 --> 03:24.390
Rong Xian is not in the valley today.

03:24.530 --> 03:25.810
Did you see him?

03:25.920 --> 03:27.130
The Sect Leader of Kunlun is seriously ill.

03:27.160 --> 03:28.480
He rushed back to Kunlun.

03:28.500 --> 03:29.710
He went back to Kunlun?

03:29.730 --> 03:32.200
Ling Long said something strange to me just now.

03:32.230 --> 03:34.250
She was acting a little strange today.

03:34.280 --> 03:35.320
I asked her what happened.

03:35.340 --> 03:36.220
She said she was tired

03:36.240 --> 03:37.310
and wanted to rest.

03:45.660 --> 03:46.340
Ling Long.

03:48.380 --> 03:49.430
Where did she go?

03:55.210 --> 03:56.910
[To Wu]

04:03.380 --> 04:04.380
Wu.

04:04.430 --> 04:06.000
Forgive me for leaving without saying goodbye.

04:06.740 --> 04:08.020
Every saintess of the Fox Clan

04:08.050 --> 04:09.540
has the jade of the tribe.

04:09.620 --> 04:10.620
When the jade cracks,

04:10.650 --> 04:12.220
it means the clan is in trouble.

04:12.410 --> 04:14.050
As the Saintess of the Fox Clan,

04:14.150 --> 04:15.910
it's my duty to protect the Fox Clan.

04:16.700 --> 04:17.760
But you're different.

04:18.160 --> 04:20.050
You left the Fox Clan with me for three years

04:20.070 --> 04:22.150
and are finally living a free and stable life.

04:22.750 --> 04:24.960
I don't want you to be in danger.

04:25.060 --> 04:27.840
I just hope you can be a carefree little girl

04:27.880 --> 04:30.030
and live a happy life

04:30.240 --> 04:32.270
with the person you love.

04:33.140 --> 04:34.830
Rong Xian and Ling Long left one after the other.

04:35.450 --> 04:37.159
I'm afraid that something will happen to the two tries today.

04:37.970 --> 04:40.060
She really mistook me for Wu.

04:41.420 --> 04:42.400
Fan Yue.

04:42.800 --> 04:44.640
Is there really nothing we can change?

04:56.120 --> 04:57.640
Is Ling Long pregnant?

04:58.090 --> 04:59.440
Let's go to the Fox Clan.

05:00.750 --> 05:09.040
[Kunlun]

05:11.450 --> 05:12.360
Rong Xian.

05:12.390 --> 05:13.880
The Sect Leader exhausted his spiritual power and died

05:13.900 --> 05:15.290
to pass on his skills to you.

05:15.320 --> 05:16.120
How dare you

05:16.140 --> 05:17.420
betray your master

05:17.450 --> 05:18.590
and the Kunlun Sect?

05:18.620 --> 05:20.890
Betray my master and the sect?

05:20.910 --> 05:23.180
The Kunlun Sect is so cruel and cold-blooded.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.830
So what if I destroy it?

05:36.900 --> 05:37.700
Rong Xian!

05:37.730 --> 05:38.440
Stop!

05:51.980 --> 05:53.490
Kunlun is wrong.

05:53.510 --> 05:54.740
But only the Kunlun Sect Leader and those

05:54.770 --> 05:56.070
four bastards deserve to die.

05:56.100 --> 05:57.630
These disciples didn't hurt you.

05:57.840 --> 05:59.370
Not everyone deserves to die!

05:59.760 --> 06:00.980
Let me ask you then.

06:01.440 --> 06:03.470
What did Ling Long and the child do wrong?

06:03.500 --> 06:04.620
Mr. Rong Xian.

06:05.210 --> 06:06.460
If you continue to kill,

06:06.690 --> 06:08.340
there's no turning back.

06:08.370 --> 06:09.250
Turn back?

06:10.150 --> 06:11.660
I'm long past the point of return.

06:12.840 --> 06:14.410
The Fox Clan was destroyed by me.

06:14.870 --> 06:16.330
I've already made a big mistake.

06:17.600 --> 06:19.880
I want this Kunlun Sect which deceived the world

06:19.920 --> 06:22.030
to be buried with Ling Long and the child!

06:22.280 --> 06:24.190
When I've killed those who deserve it,

06:24.840 --> 06:26.590
I will accompany them to hell.

06:59.690 --> 07:01.100
This child...

07:03.890 --> 07:04.890
Could it be...

07:27.320 --> 07:28.030
Ling Long!

07:32.740 --> 07:33.530
Ling Long!

07:33.980 --> 07:34.659
Ling Long!

07:35.980 --> 07:36.920
Ling Long!

07:40.120 --> 07:41.510
We're still too late.

07:43.150 --> 07:44.990
Who slaughtered the Fox Clan?

07:46.740 --> 07:47.830
Wu.

07:49.280 --> 07:50.530
Thank goodness

07:50.560 --> 07:51.710
you're alive.

07:52.640 --> 07:53.840
It's Rong Xian.

07:54.159 --> 07:56.360
Rong Xian slaughtered the Fox Clan.

07:56.750 --> 07:58.110
All of this

07:58.270 --> 07:59.960
is the Kunlun Sect's

08:00.690 --> 08:02.040
fault.

08:07.750 --> 08:08.690
Why?

08:09.980 --> 08:11.810
Isn't Rong Xian an Eternal?

08:12.390 --> 08:14.240
Wasn't Kunlun supposed to protect the people?

08:16.180 --> 08:18.190
He killed the Fox Clan.

08:18.920 --> 08:20.890
Why did he still have so much resentment

08:20.920 --> 08:22.880
to create such a realm of resentment?

08:28.600 --> 08:29.400
A realm of resentment?

08:32.679 --> 08:33.600
Yes.

08:33.929 --> 08:35.320
This is a realm of resentment.

08:36.039 --> 08:37.740
Since everything is fake,

08:38.200 --> 08:40.120
can life and death be reversed?

08:41.240 --> 08:43.270
If we save Ling Long and the baby,

08:43.289 --> 08:44.810
will there be a chance for change?

08:45.790 --> 08:46.860
Ling Long is dead.

08:47.630 --> 08:48.320
I can’t save her.

08:49.220 --> 08:51.030
You only said you couldn’t save Ling Long.

08:52.190 --> 08:53.630
So the baby can be saved?

09:01.500 --> 09:02.840
This child has gathered almost

09:02.840 --> 09:04.150
all of Ling Long's spiritual power.

09:04.710 --> 09:06.090
He can be saved.

09:06.330 --> 09:07.720
But this is just a realm of
illusion.

09:07.740 --> 09:09.710
They were already killed by Rong Xian.

09:10.040 --> 09:11.180
Even if we go against fate

09:11.210 --> 09:12.580
and save him,

09:12.600 --> 09:13.960
what good will that do?

09:13.990 --> 09:14.840
No.

09:15.520 --> 09:17.330
If everything happened

09:17.350 --> 09:18.990
as Rong Xian wished,

09:19.020 --> 09:20.130
why did he still develop

09:20.160 --> 09:21.490
such a strong resentment

09:21.520 --> 09:23.270
and such a vivid realm of resentment?

09:24.180 --> 09:25.180
You once asked me

09:25.200 --> 09:27.060
what kind of person Rong Xian was.

09:27.110 --> 09:28.490
I can see that

09:28.510 --> 09:29.680
his love for Ling Long

09:29.710 --> 09:30.660
was real.

09:31.310 --> 09:32.360
A thousand years later,

09:32.360 --> 09:33.950
what we heard was not the truth.

09:33.970 --> 09:35.380
So what we see now

09:35.420 --> 09:36.830
is not necessarily true.

09:37.820 --> 09:39.990
If the Fox Clan was destroyed before Kunlun,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.150
then who was the one

09:42.730 --> 09:43.820
who destroyed Kunlun?

09:46.540 --> 09:47.340
Fan Yue.

09:47.950 --> 09:49.370
Save this child,

09:49.630 --> 09:51.330
and everything may turn around.

09:52.390 --> 09:54.080
Do you really want to save this child?

10:19.140 --> 10:20.110
Rong Xian.

10:20.500 --> 10:22.140
Ling Long loved you so much.

10:22.170 --> 10:23.560
So why did you

10:23.580 --> 10:24.550
slaughter the Fox Clan first

10:24.600 --> 10:25.870
and then destroy the Kunlun Sect?

10:25.870 --> 10:26.910
Shut up.

10:27.910 --> 10:28.960
Shut up!

10:29.090 --> 10:31.000
The Sect Leader of Kunlun altered his memories.

10:31.020 --> 10:32.740
As a result, he hated the Fox Clan and the Saintess.

10:32.770 --> 10:34.290
That’s why he slaughtered the Fox Clan.

10:34.310 --> 10:35.710
When Saintess Ling Long died,

10:35.740 --> 10:36.580
she used her blood

10:36.600 --> 10:38.050
to recover his memories.

10:39.050 --> 10:40.190
I see.

10:41.070 --> 10:42.060
Rong Xian.

10:42.240 --> 10:43.000
Look.

10:43.610 --> 10:45.430
This is the child of you and Ling Long.

10:48.460 --> 10:51.320
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

10:49.600 --> 10:50.950
He's not.

10:51.470 --> 10:52.680
He's not!

10:52.160 --> 10:54.700
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

10:53.180 --> 10:54.570
He's dead!

10:55.360 --> 10:59.280
♫I remember that word of concern♫

10:55.790 --> 10:56.990
It was me.

10:57.130 --> 11:00.400
I killed my own wife and child!

10:59.910 --> 11:03.040
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

11:01.910 --> 11:02.970
He has gone mad.

11:03.650 --> 11:06.300
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

11:03.980 --> 11:05.470
It's useless to say anything.

11:07.260 --> 11:10.510
♫It dried in the wind♫

11:09.140 --> 11:10.170
Trust me.

11:10.960 --> 11:12.320
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

11:13.060 --> 11:16.560
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

11:17.480 --> 11:20.890
♫That year, that year♫

11:18.390 --> 11:18.990
No.

11:19.420 --> 11:20.620
The child is still here.

11:21.380 --> 11:22.140
Look.

11:21.480 --> 11:24.830
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

11:23.110 --> 11:24.510
He can cry.

11:24.680 --> 11:25.680
He can smile.

11:25.250 --> 11:28.960
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

11:26.150 --> 11:27.350
He's warm.

11:27.370 --> 11:28.670
He's breathing.

11:28.690 --> 11:30.080
He's even a little chubby.

11:29.510 --> 11:32.310
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

11:30.600 --> 11:32.840
He's soft like a little dumpling.

11:32.680 --> 11:36.170
♫That year, that year♫

11:34.210 --> 11:35.720
You haven't seen

11:36.300 --> 11:37.690
or hugged him yet.

11:36.630 --> 11:39.990
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

11:40.150 --> 11:42.220
Ling Long knew from the beginning

11:40.520 --> 11:43.800
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

11:42.700 --> 11:44.460
that this child was underdeveloped

11:44.520 --> 11:45.930
and may not live.

11:44.710 --> 11:47.750
♫Layer after layer♫

11:46.620 --> 11:49.170
But she was willing to sacrifice everything to protect him.

11:48.160 --> 11:51.810
♫Another year passed♫

11:50.790 --> 11:52.540
Because she loved this child

11:53.130 --> 11:54.120
and she loved you.

11:59.530 --> 12:02.350
♫That year, that year♫

11:59.650 --> 12:00.410
Long.

12:01.300 --> 12:02.870
I know the Fox Clan is your home.

12:03.180 --> 12:06.230
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

12:03.660 --> 12:05.140
One day,

12:05.160 --> 12:06.590
when the Eternals and demons stop fighting,

12:06.980 --> 12:08.860
when they can accept our relationship,

12:07.100 --> 12:10.240
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

12:10.010 --> 12:12.460
I will bring you back to the Fox Clan with dignity.

12:11.260 --> 12:13.640
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

12:12.490 --> 12:13.730
There shouldn't be only hatred

12:13.750 --> 12:15.540
between the demons and Eternals.

12:14.380 --> 12:17.500
♫That year, that year♫

12:15.620 --> 12:17.800
It's not wrong for us to love and protect each other.

12:17.950 --> 12:20.390
Whether Kunlun and Fox Clan accept it or not,

12:18.280 --> 12:21.410
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

12:20.740 --> 12:22.980
You, me,

12:22.120 --> 12:25.220
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

12:23.210 --> 12:25.130
and our future child

12:25.150 --> 12:26.750
are dignified.

12:26.540 --> 12:29.120
♫Layer after layer♫

12:27.500 --> 12:28.880
The world is too big.

12:29.240 --> 12:31.260
I'm tired of the fight between the two clans.

12:30.210 --> 12:33.130
♫Another year passed♫

12:31.420 --> 12:32.420
What I want

12:33.280 --> 12:35.170
is a warm home.

12:37.910 --> 12:39.900
You think you were not determined enough

12:40.030 --> 12:41.590
for falling into Kunlun's trap.

12:42.140 --> 12:44.300
You think you are the culprit.

12:44.760 --> 12:46.260
So what you hate the most

12:47.040 --> 12:48.380
is yourself,

12:48.990 --> 12:49.640
right?

12:51.290 --> 12:52.090
Why?

12:54.870 --> 12:56.990
Why am I the Saint son of Kunlun?

12:57.970 --> 13:00.670
Why must Eternals and demons fight each other to the bitter end?

13:02.020 --> 13:04.130
Why must such a cruel thing

13:04.180 --> 13:07.300
happen to me and Ling Long?

13:07.880 --> 13:10.510
There are many things in this world that cannot be explained.

13:11.730 --> 13:13.580
I also experienced injustice.

13:15.150 --> 13:16.880
I once asked Heaven

13:16.240 --> 13:21.200
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

13:19.350 --> 13:21.740
why I was saved by a deity

13:23.630 --> 13:26.040
while my older sister went missing.

13:24.360 --> 13:29.860
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

13:26.790 --> 13:28.790
Why did my father have to die?

13:30.290 --> 13:32.220
But no one can give me an answer.

13:32.650 --> 13:40.080
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

13:33.420 --> 13:34.910
Maybe most people in the world

13:35.360 --> 13:37.050
are suffering.

13:37.420 --> 13:38.770
We all have our own sufferings.

13:39.900 --> 13:42.450
But we have to find a way for ourselves.

13:41.000 --> 13:46.050
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

13:45.570 --> 13:47.720
If my path is to go on,

13:50.070 --> 13:51.330
your path

13:52.590 --> 13:53.680
is to let go.

14:05.120 --> 14:08.680
♫Across thousands of miles♫

14:13.450 --> 14:18.060
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

14:20.770 --> 14:28.040
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

14:29.110 --> 14:33.780
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

14:34.670 --> 14:36.240
You look like your mother.

14:37.410 --> 14:38.340
Not like me.

14:39.890 --> 14:40.940
It's good.

14:53.260 --> 14:58.650
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

14:57.890 --> 14:59.200
Child.

15:01.290 --> 15:06.850
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees♫

15:01.650 --> 15:03.470
There's too much resentment here.

15:03.970 --> 15:05.320
Let's go to your mother.

15:06.410 --> 15:07.290
Okay?

15:09.790 --> 15:16.760
♫ To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart ♫

15:17.260 --> 15:22.450
♫I'm your wanderer♫

15:26.030 --> 15:30.580
♫The flowers flew away♫

15:33.730 --> 15:39.240
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

15:42.810 --> 15:45.830
[Wuji Palace]

15:44.590 --> 15:46.480
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

15:46.620 --> 15:48.790
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

15:48.850 --> 15:50.640
♫My love brought tears♫

15:50.890 --> 15:52.740
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

15:53.090 --> 15:54.670
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

15:55.040 --> 15:56.650
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

15:55.190 --> 15:57.970
[Wuji Palace]

15:56.520 --> 15:57.850
His resentment is dissolving.

15:56.940 --> 15:58.950
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

15:59.050 --> 16:00.210
We can get out soon!

15:59.260 --> 16:00.840
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

16:01.160 --> 16:02.950
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

16:03.220 --> 16:05.230
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

16:05.520 --> 16:07.020
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

16:07.220 --> 16:09.680
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

16:23.150 --> 16:23.980
Cang Shan.

16:24.350 --> 16:25.280
Cang Shan!

16:32.410 --> 16:33.670
I can finally move.

16:46.330 --> 16:47.210
Shuo!

16:48.360 --> 16:49.520
-Master!
-Master!

16:50.240 --> 16:51.300
What happened?

16:52.020 --> 16:52.880
Shuo.

16:53.070 --> 16:53.910
Are you okay?

16:55.680 --> 16:56.400
What happened?

16:56.430 --> 16:57.190
I'm fine.

16:57.780 --> 16:59.450
We entered Rong Xian's realm of resentment.

16:59.470 --> 17:00.530
In the realm of resentment,

17:00.550 --> 17:01.580
we changed some things.

17:02.140 --> 17:03.250
For the past 1,000 years,

17:03.270 --> 17:04.940
Rong Xian had a painful life.

17:05.680 --> 17:07.200
He created this realm of resentment

17:07.230 --> 17:09.380
and repeated the tragedy again and again.

17:09.400 --> 17:11.400
He did it to punish himself.

17:11.430 --> 17:13.190
But he must have silently hoped

17:13.359 --> 17:15.800
that someone could come and save him.

17:18.800 --> 17:19.560
Fan Yue.

17:20.290 --> 17:21.160
Thank you

17:21.680 --> 17:22.770
for saving the child

17:22.790 --> 17:24.020
and Rong Xian.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.810
He saved the child himself.

17:27.119 --> 17:28.569
He couldn't forgive himself.

17:28.730 --> 17:30.200
That's why he'd been obsessed for 1000 years.

17:30.900 --> 17:32.630
But even when the tragedies were set in stone

17:32.650 --> 17:34.040
and the past couldn't be changed,

17:34.120 --> 17:35.210
he still hoped that

17:35.230 --> 17:36.450
someone could change the child's fate

17:36.470 --> 17:38.000
in the realm of resentment.

17:38.510 --> 17:40.420
That's why it was possible to save him.

17:40.450 --> 17:41.740
He chose us.

17:43.900 --> 17:45.590
Rong Xian hated himself for a thousand years.

17:46.620 --> 17:48.180
Now he can finally let it go.

17:48.850 --> 17:49.490
Hey.

17:49.510 --> 17:50.070
They've been

17:50.100 --> 17:50.930
mumbling for a while.

17:50.950 --> 17:51.710
What are they talking about?

17:52.090 --> 17:53.160
If you want to know,

17:53.180 --> 17:54.140
ask them yourself.

18:15.150 --> 18:16.310
It's the Heart Flame.

18:16.550 --> 18:17.390
It's really the Heart Flame.

18:17.420 --> 18:18.160
There it is.

18:18.430 --> 18:19.420
The Heart Flame has appeared.

18:19.450 --> 18:20.410
This is the Heart Flame.

18:20.430 --> 18:21.520
Is it really the Heart Flame?

18:30.770 --> 18:31.880
How could it be?

18:31.910 --> 18:32.790
Mu Jiu.

18:33.220 --> 18:34.220
Take it.

18:34.530 --> 18:35.850
-Senior.
-Senior.

18:37.130 --> 18:38.600
This was Mr. Rong Xian's choice.

18:38.810 --> 18:39.710
He also hoped that

18:39.740 --> 18:41.380
we could let go of the two clans' hatred.

18:41.780 --> 18:42.290
Otherwise,

18:42.320 --> 18:43.760
we wouldn't have switched identities

18:43.780 --> 18:45.220
in the realm of resentment.

18:45.820 --> 18:47.740
This Heart Flame belongs to the Fox Clan now.

18:47.760 --> 18:48.630
Kunlun has no objections.

18:48.660 --> 18:49.420
No.

18:50.110 --> 18:51.820
Everyone contributed to exploring the Outlanders' Tomb.

18:51.960 --> 18:53.090
Why does he get to keep it?

18:53.120 --> 18:53.430
That's right.

18:53.450 --> 18:54.180
Exactly!

18:54.240 --> 18:55.710
Why does he get to keep it?

18:55.740 --> 18:56.500
Exactly.

18:56.520 --> 18:57.590
A man who has been dead for a thousand years

18:57.620 --> 18:58.590
has no right

18:58.610 --> 19:00.050
to decide the ownership of the Heart Flame for the living.

19:00.080 --> 19:00.920
That's right!

19:00.940 --> 19:01.730
Enough.

19:01.760 --> 19:03.240
I didn't want it at first.

19:03.640 --> 19:04.920
But now that you are

19:04.950 --> 19:05.950
all fighting for it,

19:06.340 --> 19:07.800
I won't part with it anymore.

19:07.820 --> 19:08.960
Let me tell you.

19:08.990 --> 19:10.520
Whoever dares to fight me for it

19:10.540 --> 19:12.380
will be the enemy of Jingyou Mountain.

19:13.270 --> 19:14.790
His aunt is Chang Mei.

19:14.820 --> 19:15.930
Chang Mei is one of the Three Kings of the Demon Race.

19:15.950 --> 19:16.630
She's quite formidable

19:16.660 --> 19:17.810
and not easy to deal with.

19:17.880 --> 19:19.430
You guys might be scared of Chang Mei,

19:19.570 --> 19:21.600
but the Yunxiao Sect is not.

19:21.810 --> 19:22.600
Kid.

19:23.330 --> 19:25.120
Give me the second Heart Flame.

19:26.790 --> 19:28.040
As you can see,

19:28.850 --> 19:31.260
you can’t keep the Heart Flame for even half a day.

19:31.280 --> 19:32.600
Why don’t you give it to me?

19:32.930 --> 19:33.820
Why should I give it to you?

19:35.540 --> 19:36.980
But this lady

19:37.000 --> 19:38.560
saved me from chaos just now.

19:38.810 --> 19:39.810
If you want it,

19:40.190 --> 19:41.300
I can think about it.

19:43.720 --> 19:44.480
Her?

19:46.810 --> 19:47.860
No.

19:48.940 --> 19:50.700
When you fought Rong Xian just now,

19:50.730 --> 19:52.010
you obviously used spiritual power.

19:52.960 --> 19:54.340
You are not a demon.

19:54.610 --> 19:55.960
-Yes.
-You're an Outlander.

19:56.390 --> 19:57.390
-An Outlander?
-What do you mean?

19:57.410 --> 19:58.230
Yes.

19:58.920 --> 20:00.380
My identity

20:00.410 --> 20:01.650
has nothing to do with you.

20:01.700 --> 20:03.490
Bright Moon Palace cheated.

20:03.740 --> 20:05.210
How could it have nothing to do with us?

20:05.240 --> 20:05.890
That's right.

20:05.910 --> 20:07.180
That's right.

20:07.790 --> 20:08.480
How can you cheat?

20:08.480 --> 20:09.280
Master Fan.

20:09.310 --> 20:10.480
You brought a human to the tournament.

20:10.500 --> 20:11.650
We've put up with it.

20:11.680 --> 20:12.640
Right?

20:12.660 --> 20:14.870
Now you colluded with an Outlander to cheat.

20:14.900 --> 20:16.730
How can we accept that?

20:16.750 --> 20:17.400
Right?

20:17.440 --> 20:18.720
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

20:18.720 --> 20:20.240
Tian Huo left Outlanders' City seven years ago.

20:20.260 --> 20:21.830
She's no longer informed about matters of Outlanders' City.

20:21.860 --> 20:23.170
She's now taking the demonic path

20:23.200 --> 20:24.250
and practicing demonic magic.

20:24.270 --> 20:25.620
She joined the tournament as a demon.

20:25.650 --> 20:26.570
What's wrong with that?

20:26.600 --> 20:27.880
She can change her skillset,

20:27.900 --> 20:29.270
but can she change her bloodline?

20:29.300 --> 20:29.970
She is an Outlander

20:29.990 --> 20:31.030
in her bones.

20:31.990 --> 20:32.800
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

20:32.820 --> 20:33.820
Ugly.

20:34.560 --> 20:36.010
And you...

20:36.250 --> 20:37.380
Purple Potato Spirit.

20:37.410 --> 20:38.930
You failed to obtain the Heart Flame,

20:38.950 --> 20:40.090
and now you're picking on her origins.

20:40.120 --> 20:41.810
To think you were referring to yourselves

20:41.830 --> 20:43.500
as elites among demons and Eternals.

20:43.530 --> 20:44.810
I think you're all just

20:44.830 --> 20:46.350
shameless!

20:46.640 --> 20:48.040
-You want to die?
-You want to die?

20:48.070 --> 20:48.880
What did you say?

20:49.750 --> 20:50.740
Stop! Come here!

20:52.790 --> 20:53.990
-Come here.
-Stop!

20:54.110 --> 20:55.460
-Stop!
-Go after him!

20:55.860 --> 20:57.960
-Stop!
-Stop!

20:58.200 --> 20:59.310
He has the Heart Flame.

20:59.310 --> 21:00.200
Aren't you going to chase him?

21:12.610 --> 21:13.400
Don't let him escape.

21:13.400 --> 21:13.920
Stop!

21:13.920 --> 21:14.830
-Stop!
-Stop!

21:14.830 --> 21:15.400
Stop!

21:15.400 --> 21:16.270
Stop!

21:16.270 --> 21:17.090
Stop!

21:17.830 --> 21:18.590
Stop!

21:20.940 --> 21:21.820
Stop!

21:22.480 --> 21:23.390
Catch him!

21:23.670 --> 21:24.560
Stop!

21:27.220 --> 21:28.450
Bunch of idiots.

21:28.890 --> 21:30.260
You'll never catch me.

21:32.390 --> 21:34.810
The famous Lady Tian Huo of the Demon Race

21:35.210 --> 21:36.540
is actually an Outlander.

21:38.340 --> 21:39.560
Interesting.

21:47.580 --> 21:48.170
Master.

21:48.200 --> 21:49.830
Why don’t we take the Heart Flame

21:49.830 --> 21:50.720
from Mu Jiu?

21:55.160 --> 21:55.750
Master!

21:55.750 --> 21:56.960
-Master!
-Master!

21:59.990 --> 22:01.060
I’m fine.

22:01.700 --> 22:03.320
I’m just a little injured.

22:03.790 --> 22:06.080
That wasn't the best time to take the Heart Flame.

22:06.110 --> 22:07.640
The third Heart Flame hasn't been found.

22:07.940 --> 22:09.940
If we have both Heart Flames in our hands,

22:10.130 --> 22:12.210
we will only become the next target.

22:12.560 --> 22:13.270
Master.

22:13.300 --> 22:15.430
What happened in the realm of resentment?

22:15.490 --> 22:17.290
How did you get hurt so badly?

22:19.660 --> 22:20.310
I'm fine.

22:21.310 --> 22:22.240
I just expended some mana

22:22.240 --> 22:24.050
changing fate in the realm of resentment.

22:24.080 --> 22:25.430
Just some mana?

22:25.850 --> 22:27.240
Even in the realm of resentment,

22:27.270 --> 22:28.600
the price of changing fate

22:28.620 --> 22:30.750
is a severe injury at best and death at worst.

22:30.770 --> 22:32.200
You're speaking too lightly of it.

22:32.230 --> 22:32.940
Master.

22:32.970 --> 22:34.410
You have the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on you.

22:34.430 --> 22:35.840
Why don’t you cherish yourself more?

22:37.120 --> 22:37.830
Did you do all that

22:37.830 --> 22:39.070
to save Bai Shuo?

22:40.010 --> 22:41.760
I just wanted to escape the realm of resentment.

22:42.140 --> 22:43.620
How could it have been to save Bai Shuo?

22:44.510 --> 22:45.830
Then, does Bai Shuo know that

22:46.570 --> 22:48.600
to destroy Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

22:48.680 --> 22:49.870
you greatly damaged your spiritual power?

22:49.900 --> 22:51.030
She doesn't know yet.

22:52.000 --> 22:53.670
Don't mention it to her either.

22:56.880 --> 22:57.920
-Yes.
-Yes.

23:01.960 --> 23:05.350
[Please send help, Grand Master. From: Chong Zhao]

23:08.310 --> 23:09.110
Senior.

23:09.140 --> 23:09.930
You called?

23:10.710 --> 23:12.300
We can't use magic to send letters within Outlanders' City.

23:12.330 --> 23:13.580
Go outside the city

23:13.710 --> 23:14.740
and send this letter

23:14.160 --> 23:17.840
[To Sect Leader]

23:14.880 --> 23:16.250
to our sect with your spiritual power.

23:16.530 --> 23:17.780
Send a letter?

23:18.030 --> 23:19.150
Why so sudden?

23:19.170 --> 23:20.170
Within Outlanders' City,

23:20.200 --> 23:21.310
be it that unknown monster,

23:21.350 --> 23:22.510
Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

23:22.540 --> 23:23.690
or that Tian Huo,

23:23.710 --> 23:25.230
they are all too suspicious.

23:25.830 --> 23:28.100
I'm afraid the Wutong Martial Arts Contest isn't just a simple contest.

23:28.720 --> 23:29.550
Hurry back.

23:29.570 --> 23:30.530
Don't let anyone find out.

24:06.590 --> 24:08.080
[To Sect Leader]

24:13.440 --> 24:17.730
[To Sect Leader]

24:17.750 --> 24:21.450
[Please send help, Grand Master. From: Chong Zhao]

24:19.930 --> 24:20.650
Your Majesty,

24:21.510 --> 24:23.270
Chong Zhao did report to Lanling Sect.

24:23.300 --> 24:24.650
Fortunately, I was prepared

24:24.670 --> 24:25.560
and intercepted the letter.

24:26.400 --> 24:27.530
Zhen Yu was right.

24:27.550 --> 24:28.620
The Contemplation Stone

24:28.650 --> 24:30.610
can indeed bring them into Rong Xian's realm of resentment.

24:31.350 --> 24:32.430
A thousand years ago,

24:32.800 --> 24:34.680
Rong Xian hated the Eternals and demons.

24:35.030 --> 24:36.550
He brought Ling Long’s body

24:36.570 --> 24:37.750
to Outlanders' City.

24:38.160 --> 24:39.680
After burying his wife and child,

24:40.430 --> 24:42.190
he committed suicide in front of the tomb

24:42.610 --> 24:44.260
and left 1000 years of resentment.

24:44.320 --> 24:45.920
No one managed to resolve it.

24:46.260 --> 24:47.700
Fan Yue and Bai Shuo

24:47.730 --> 24:49.290
thought they had resolved

24:49.310 --> 24:50.660
Rong Xian's resentment.

24:51.980 --> 24:53.390
But they don't know

24:54.290 --> 24:56.530
that they're just paving the way for us.

24:58.020 --> 24:59.310
Has Fu Ling's operation

24:59.340 --> 25:00.100
started?

25:00.120 --> 25:00.980
According to the plan,

25:01.010 --> 25:01.860
it should start soon.

25:02.290 --> 25:04.320
The Fenlan Banquet is in two days.

25:04.600 --> 25:06.330
The moment the Eternals and demons enter the palace,

25:06.460 --> 25:07.500
they will

25:07.530 --> 25:08.880
never get to leave again.

25:09.330 --> 25:10.480
The last banquet,

25:11.030 --> 25:12.420
an arena of life and death.

25:14.110 --> 25:17.500
I will give them the grandest funeral.

25:18.890 --> 25:19.680
Master!

25:19.710 --> 25:20.400
-Master!
-Master!

25:21.600 --> 25:22.280
How could this happen?

25:22.300 --> 25:23.170
Changing fate

25:23.200 --> 25:24.410
is not a trivial matter.

25:24.440 --> 25:26.360
I'm afraid it has hurt your core.

25:26.380 --> 25:28.030
Bai Shuo learned some medical skills from Old Turtle.

25:28.060 --> 25:29.000
Go get her.

25:29.380 --> 25:30.000
Okay.

25:31.380 --> 25:32.290
Master.

25:35.840 --> 25:36.820
I brought the medicine.

25:36.850 --> 25:38.250
Quick, treat our master.

25:41.180 --> 25:42.460
What happened to him?

25:42.480 --> 25:43.480
When did he get hurt?

25:43.510 --> 25:45.420
You don't even know when he got hurt?

25:45.440 --> 25:46.500
He used up so much demonic power

25:46.520 --> 25:47.760
to reverse that child's fate

25:47.790 --> 25:49.030
in the realm of resentment for you.

25:49.050 --> 25:49.480
But you don't even...

25:49.480 --> 25:50.030
Cang Shan.

25:58.030 --> 25:58.550
[Rejuvenation Pill]

26:03.020 --> 26:04.060
What is this pill?

26:04.680 --> 26:05.480
Rejuvenation Pill.

26:05.480 --> 26:06.130
Second grade.

26:06.160 --> 26:07.150
It can replenish the spiritual core.

26:08.470 --> 26:09.330
If you don't believe me,

26:09.350 --> 26:10.560
then just watch him die.

26:33.500 --> 26:34.370
It really works.

26:34.390 --> 26:35.710
This pill is not enough.

26:35.730 --> 26:37.140
We still need some medicine.

26:37.160 --> 26:38.570
Go find the medicine in the city.

26:38.590 --> 26:39.110
Prescriptions?

26:59.260 --> 27:00.220
Fan Yue.

27:00.780 --> 27:02.220
Save this child,

27:02.520 --> 27:04.420
and everything may turn around.

27:20.180 --> 27:22.600
Saving that child would damage your demonic power.

27:23.310 --> 27:24.950
Why didn't you tell me that

27:25.020 --> 27:26.130
in the realm of resentment?

27:31.590 --> 27:32.430
Fan Yue,

27:33.590 --> 27:35.550
what kind of person are you?

28:27.570 --> 28:28.370
Tian Huo!

28:28.400 --> 28:29.360
Cang Shan!

28:31.220 --> 28:32.220
What's wrong?

28:32.660 --> 28:33.890
Is your master awake?

28:33.920 --> 28:35.290
We didn't hear him summon us.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.550
He's not in the room.

28:38.860 --> 28:39.920
Master?

28:39.940 --> 28:40.620
Where is he?

28:40.650 --> 28:41.900
He's injured and weak.

28:41.920 --> 28:43.560
He could have at least brought me along.

28:43.580 --> 28:45.210
There is no sign of an outsider entering.

28:45.240 --> 28:47.000
He left the room by himself.

28:47.020 --> 28:48.180
Let's split up and search.

28:48.210 --> 28:48.660
Let's go.

28:49.550 --> 28:50.350
This way.

28:59.920 --> 29:00.750
Excuse me.

29:00.750 --> 29:02.070
Take a look.

29:10.200 --> 29:10.980
Be careful!

29:15.950 --> 29:17.060
I'm sorry, Miss.

29:17.550 --> 29:19.510
I didn't spend the whole night saving you

29:19.530 --> 29:21.000
to let you get hit by a log.

29:21.030 --> 29:22.160
Why didn't you dodge?

29:25.090 --> 29:26.940
Why is he staring at me?

29:27.080 --> 29:28.450
Is he angry because

29:28.470 --> 29:29.460
I scolded him too harshly?

29:31.030 --> 29:32.450
Since you're fine,

29:33.060 --> 29:34.150
I'll go back first.

29:42.950 --> 29:43.910
Does it hurt?

29:50.530 --> 29:51.610
You're not Fan Yue.

29:52.120 --> 29:52.960
Who are you?

29:59.930 --> 30:02.350
You really don't remember your name?

30:05.370 --> 30:06.030
What about

30:06.030 --> 30:06.960
Bright Moon Palace?

30:09.400 --> 30:10.640
The Demon King of the Polar Region?

30:12.820 --> 30:13.770
Tian Huo and Cang Shan?

30:16.400 --> 30:18.660
You must remember the Contemplation Stone, right?

30:19.920 --> 30:21.750
What do you remember?

30:21.770 --> 30:22.630
You.

30:24.180 --> 30:24.780
You...

30:25.390 --> 30:26.840
You remember who I am?

30:27.740 --> 30:28.620
You are...

30:28.880 --> 30:29.750
Someone kind

30:30.510 --> 30:31.450
who saved me.

30:31.890 --> 30:33.720
What's wrong with him?

30:33.750 --> 30:35.470
I only fed him the Rejuvenation Pill last night.

30:35.490 --> 30:36.520
Nothing wrong with that.

30:36.740 --> 30:38.700
Is it because he was injured in the realm of resentment

30:38.750 --> 30:39.670
and the nature was different,

30:39.700 --> 30:41.220
so it changed the effect of the pill?

30:41.840 --> 30:42.630
No.

30:42.650 --> 30:44.380
Tian Huo and Cang Shan can never know that

30:44.410 --> 30:45.810
I turned Fan Yue into a fool.

30:45.830 --> 30:47.430
Otherwise, they will kill me.

30:49.830 --> 30:51.270
Listen.

30:51.290 --> 30:52.850
Your name is Fan Yue,

30:52.880 --> 30:55.570
Demon King of Polar Region and Master of Bright Moon Palace.

30:55.600 --> 30:57.650
Tian Huo and Cang Shan are your

30:57.680 --> 30:58.680
two generals.

30:58.680 --> 30:59.400
Your reputation

30:59.400 --> 31:00.720
is known to the world,

31:00.720 --> 31:01.810
and feared by everyone.

31:01.830 --> 31:03.550
Your home is in Bright Moon Palace.

31:03.580 --> 31:05.140
You spent a lot of money to build it.

31:05.160 --> 31:06.480
It's very grand and luxurious,

31:06.500 --> 31:08.070
just like your clothes.

31:08.100 --> 31:09.970
And we are in Outlanders' City right now,

31:10.030 --> 31:12.200
We're here to activate the Contemplation Stone.

31:20.530 --> 31:21.960
We've searched the whole Outlanders' City,

31:21.980 --> 31:23.220
but Master is nowhere to be found.

31:23.250 --> 31:24.570
Is he back already?

31:25.880 --> 31:26.710
Guests,

31:26.730 --> 31:27.580
your master

31:27.610 --> 31:28.560
came back long ago.

31:28.590 --> 31:29.270
I saw

31:29.270 --> 31:30.360
the human girl

31:30.390 --> 31:31.430
drag him upstairs.

31:35.680 --> 31:36.860
My name is Bai Shuo.

31:36.960 --> 31:38.000
I'm your...

31:40.740 --> 31:41.350
Lover.

31:45.960 --> 31:48.120
Did I say it too fast just now?

31:48.160 --> 31:48.590
Let me repeat myself.

31:48.590 --> 31:49.200
Bai Shuo.

31:50.480 --> 31:51.240
I got it.

31:52.980 --> 31:55.510
You promised to protect me.

31:55.540 --> 31:56.820
Does it still count?

31:56.840 --> 31:57.510
Yes.

31:59.240 --> 32:00.200
A demon king's promise

32:00.200 --> 32:01.070
cannot be broken.

32:07.700 --> 32:08.540
I won't break it.

32:10.330 --> 32:13.610
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

32:14.450 --> 32:17.720
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

32:18.270 --> 32:19.590
Why do you trust me so much?

32:19.640 --> 32:22.230
♫Every starlight♫

32:19.860 --> 32:21.290
When you saved me,

32:21.610 --> 32:23.110
your eyes were full of concern.

32:22.720 --> 32:26.290
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

32:23.780 --> 32:25.500
Although I can't remember who you are,

32:25.950 --> 32:27.800
you must be the closest person to me.

32:28.430 --> 32:29.430
That's why I trust you.

32:30.400 --> 32:31.160
Shuo.

32:32.030 --> 32:32.600
Master!

32:32.630 --> 32:33.700
-Master!
-Master!

32:39.860 --> 32:40.690
You...

32:40.720 --> 32:41.370
What...

32:42.680 --> 32:43.440
Oh no.

32:43.470 --> 32:44.670
I haven't finished telling him everything.

32:44.880 --> 32:45.590
Fan Yue lost his memory.

32:45.590 --> 32:46.790
He doesn't remember them at all.

32:46.790 --> 32:47.310
They'll find out as soon as he talks.

32:47.310 --> 32:47.920
Bai Shuo.

32:47.940 --> 32:49.460
How dare you seduce our master

32:49.490 --> 32:50.500
while we're away?

32:50.520 --> 32:51.910
I was...

32:51.940 --> 32:53.020
I took the initiative.

33:01.160 --> 33:02.260
Is there a problem?

33:06.320 --> 33:07.400
If not,

33:08.050 --> 33:09.330
you can leave now.

33:09.350 --> 33:11.180
Since you are back safe and sound,

33:11.210 --> 33:12.410
we'll leave now.

33:18.130 --> 33:18.930
Close the door.

33:30.600 --> 33:31.800
They must be

33:31.820 --> 33:33.410
Tian Huo and Cang Shan, right?

33:34.320 --> 33:35.610
You don't want to see them?

33:37.010 --> 33:38.440
Why do you think so?

33:38.470 --> 33:40.040
Because when they came in,

33:40.750 --> 33:42.000
you looked anxious.

33:42.530 --> 33:43.490
It seems that

33:43.510 --> 33:44.940
even though he lost his memory,

33:44.970 --> 33:46.140
he didn't become a fool.

33:46.160 --> 33:47.710
He's still smart.

33:48.330 --> 33:49.160
Remember.

33:49.180 --> 33:50.220
Outlanders' City is dangerous.

33:50.250 --> 33:52.820
Don't let anyone find out you lost your memory,

33:52.840 --> 33:54.030
including them.

33:56.580 --> 33:57.290
How about this?

33:57.320 --> 33:58.010
I'll teach you.

34:00.910 --> 34:02.800
Just remember these words:

34:03.140 --> 34:07.280
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

34:03.640 --> 34:04.440
Stand straight,

34:05.530 --> 34:06.490
talk less,

34:06.510 --> 34:07.420
and look sharp.

34:07.890 --> 34:10.070
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

34:10.820 --> 34:14.090
♫The one who was slightly late♫

34:11.260 --> 34:13.449
Use a commanding tone when you talk to others,

34:13.480 --> 34:14.480
like this.

34:14.550 --> 34:15.380
Like this.

34:15.330 --> 34:22.409
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

34:15.590 --> 34:16.510
One more time.

34:16.840 --> 34:17.650
Like this.

34:19.929 --> 34:20.630
Stand straight.

34:20.770 --> 34:23.380
Put this hand here.

34:23.870 --> 34:26.679
♫You enriched my life♫

34:26.090 --> 34:27.889
Don't you think something is wrong with Master?

34:28.360 --> 34:29.760
Yes.

34:31.100 --> 34:32.719
Bai Shuo slept in the Master's room

34:32.750 --> 34:33.750
for one night.

34:34.610 --> 34:36.000
Do you think

34:36.020 --> 34:37.489
she drugged our Master?

34:37.510 --> 34:38.469
What did you say?

34:40.280 --> 34:42.340
Who slept in Fan Yue's room all night?

34:44.840 --> 34:45.639
I...

34:46.370 --> 34:46.969
Yes.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.239
Like this.

34:48.989 --> 34:50.199
You have to look colder

34:50.219 --> 34:51.449
and more arrogant.

34:51.480 --> 34:52.440
Your gaze must be sharper.

35:02.030 --> 35:02.720
Master of Bright Moon,

35:02.740 --> 35:03.740
please behave yourself.

35:04.100 --> 35:05.110
-How dare you be rude to our master!
-Zhao.

35:05.110 --> 35:05.800
It's not what you think.

35:09.890 --> 35:11.330
Shuo is my woman.

35:11.350 --> 35:13.070
I can do whatever I want.

35:13.100 --> 35:14.060
It’s none of your business.

35:14.080 --> 35:15.240
Let her go!

35:15.730 --> 35:16.770
Zhao, you...

35:17.810 --> 35:19.470
I only listen to Shuo.

35:19.490 --> 35:21.070
If and when I'd let go

35:21.160 --> 35:22.210
all depends on her words.

35:26.820 --> 35:27.670
Fan Yue.

35:27.820 --> 35:28.790
Let go.

35:28.810 --> 35:29.770
That's too much.

35:31.210 --> 35:32.080
Let go.

35:35.970 --> 35:37.200
Come with me.

35:45.180 --> 35:45.930
Master...

35:45.960 --> 35:46.690
Get out.

35:47.590 --> 35:48.380
Yes.

35:55.930 --> 35:56.670
Close the door.

36:05.800 --> 36:07.910
It's not what you think.

36:07.930 --> 36:10.410
Fan Yue was injured saving someone in the illusion realm.

36:10.440 --> 36:12.250
I took care of him all night.

36:12.270 --> 36:13.190
Saving someone?

36:13.710 --> 36:14.750
He is a Demon King.

36:15.490 --> 36:16.410
He'd save someone?

36:17.250 --> 36:19.130
He's not like what you think.

36:19.150 --> 36:20.340
But he just...

36:23.770 --> 36:24.520
Shuo.

36:25.370 --> 36:27.370
When did you two become so close?

36:27.780 --> 36:29.640
Fan Yue doesn't remember anything now.

36:29.670 --> 36:30.940
Anyone can kill him.

36:30.960 --> 36:32.960
I can't let anyone know that he lost his memory.

36:33.760 --> 36:34.670
Close?

36:35.670 --> 36:37.870
I just don't want to owe him anything.

36:38.110 --> 36:39.550
In Outlanders' City, Eternals and demons are in conflict

36:39.550 --> 36:40.590
while danger lurks everywhere.

36:40.890 --> 36:42.620
Have you ever thought about withdrawing from the contest?

36:43.060 --> 36:44.590
The contest is not the only chance.

36:44.620 --> 36:45.590
If something happens to you in Outlanders' City,

36:45.590 --> 36:46.960
you'll lose your life.

36:47.270 --> 36:48.710
Be it returning favors or taking revenge,

36:48.890 --> 36:50.410
I don't want to wait any longer.

36:50.440 --> 36:52.450
Even if it's a cliff ahead,

36:52.480 --> 36:53.690
I'll take the leap.

36:53.710 --> 36:54.910
What if you'll be smashed to pieces?

36:54.940 --> 36:56.090
Will you still jump?

36:58.000 --> 37:00.260
Judging from the previous stories,

37:00.280 --> 37:01.760
jumping off a cliff

37:02.250 --> 37:04.210
will always be met with a miracle.

37:04.810 --> 37:06.080
I might get a legendary weapon

37:06.100 --> 37:07.380
or acquire a unique skill,

37:07.740 --> 37:09.730
and then come back to slay my enemies

37:10.570 --> 37:11.700
and get what I want.

37:13.500 --> 37:14.270
Chong Zhao.

37:15.030 --> 37:16.600
Wish me the same.

37:17.160 --> 37:18.580
Wish me success

37:18.650 --> 37:19.990
in getting what I want.

37:21.520 --> 37:22.360
Must you stay?

37:23.160 --> 37:24.160
I must stay.

37:31.090 --> 37:32.280
I see.

37:34.760 --> 37:36.200
So what can I do for you?

37:44.630 --> 37:46.840
What did you do to Master?

37:48.540 --> 37:49.780
I knew it.

37:49.800 --> 37:51.500
It's easy to fool Cang Shan,

37:51.620 --> 37:53.050
but not you.

37:57.020 --> 37:58.110
Amnesia?

37:58.140 --> 37:59.220
Lovers?

37:59.240 --> 38:00.550
When Master regains his memory

38:00.580 --> 38:01.790
and sees through your teasing,

38:01.810 --> 38:03.130
he won't let you off easy.

38:04.160 --> 38:05.680
Don't threaten me.

38:05.710 --> 38:07.890
Your master only trusts me now.

38:07.980 --> 38:09.540
If I'm unhappy,

38:09.560 --> 38:11.820
I'll feed him one Rejuvenation Pill every day.

38:11.850 --> 38:13.690
Let's see if he trusts me, his lover,

38:13.710 --> 38:15.100
or you, his guardian.

38:15.150 --> 38:15.840
Don't you dare.

38:15.860 --> 38:16.970
Why not?

38:17.010 --> 38:18.370
The Demon King as my lover?

38:18.410 --> 38:19.710
What an honor.

38:19.740 --> 38:21.700
If you still want to gather the Five Contemplations,

38:21.720 --> 38:23.800
cure him as soon as possible.

38:23.820 --> 38:25.280
You think I don't want to?

38:25.880 --> 38:27.340
His current situation

38:27.360 --> 38:28.500
is unexpected.

38:28.530 --> 38:30.140
It takes time to cure him.

38:30.160 --> 38:31.410
How long?

38:32.440 --> 38:33.810
At least one or two days.

38:33.840 --> 38:34.680
And at most?

38:34.700 --> 38:35.700
I don't know yet.

38:37.130 --> 38:38.630
You'd better not have

38:38.820 --> 38:40.790
done this to him on purpose.

38:41.570 --> 38:43.770
I have the same goal as Fan Yue.

38:43.800 --> 38:44.950
Even now,

38:44.980 --> 38:46.500
we are still allies.

38:46.520 --> 38:48.250
I won't hurt him on purpose.

38:48.450 --> 38:50.020
You only treat him as an ally?

38:55.290 --> 38:56.130
What else?

38:57.330 --> 38:58.400
I hope so.

39:04.300 --> 39:05.450
Got hurt?

39:07.160 --> 39:08.280
Tian Huo and Cang Shan

39:08.300 --> 39:10.310
were secretly searching for herbs in the city.

39:10.340 --> 39:11.790
They are all healing herbs.

39:11.810 --> 39:13.860
I'm afraid only Fan Yue can make them

39:14.040 --> 39:15.050
them so anxious.

39:15.660 --> 39:18.380
Did he get hurt in Rong Xian's realm of resentment?

39:19.200 --> 39:20.300
So,

39:20.460 --> 39:22.420
Tian Huo is not with Fan Yue now.

39:22.450 --> 39:23.220
Yes.

39:38.260 --> 39:41.160
[Sihai Inn]

39:47.400 --> 39:48.330
I just made it.

39:58.510 --> 39:59.930
Are you really angry?

40:01.640 --> 40:03.430
I was afraid Zhao would

40:03.450 --> 40:04.620
find out you lost your memory.

40:04.650 --> 40:05.730
-That's why...
-You called him Zhao,

40:05.750 --> 40:06.650
but you call me Fan Yue.

40:10.080 --> 40:11.150
Because of this?

40:15.550 --> 40:16.550
Mu.

40:16.580 --> 40:18.480
I usually call you Mu,

40:18.500 --> 40:20.070
because you have "Mu" in your written name.

40:20.100 --> 40:21.870
But you are the Demon King of the Polar Region.

40:21.890 --> 40:23.000
So I can't call you

40:23.030 --> 40:24.540
by that name in front of others.

40:26.700 --> 40:27.410
Mu.

40:27.430 --> 40:30.910
♫The person standing far away♫

40:29.530 --> 40:30.260
Take the medicine.

40:30.290 --> 40:30.880
Mu.

40:31.840 --> 40:33.570
♫Don't be afraid♫

40:34.910 --> 40:38.850
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

40:39.710 --> 40:46.020
♫Walk towards me♫

40:41.410 --> 40:42.700
Good boy.

40:42.810 --> 40:43.890
Have a good rest.

40:43.910 --> 40:44.900
Sleep early.

40:46.430 --> 40:47.390
Where are you going?

40:48.010 --> 40:48.930
To my room.

40:48.150 --> 40:51.130
♫My heart feels so...♫

40:49.130 --> 40:50.520
There's a bed here.

40:50.550 --> 40:51.590
Let's sleep together.

40:51.560 --> 40:57.160
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

40:53.300 --> 40:54.960
We can't sleep together.

40:55.250 --> 40:56.230
Why not?

40:56.250 --> 40:57.180
Look.

40:57.210 --> 40:58.320
In this inn,

40:58.340 --> 40:59.850
everyone gets a room.

40:59.110 --> 41:02.890
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

40:59.870 --> 41:00.800
Why is that so?

41:00.830 --> 41:03.140
It's to give each other some space to be alone.

41:03.160 --> 41:04.220
We're lovers.

41:04.250 --> 41:05.260
Why should we be alone?

41:05.290 --> 41:06.040
Love...

41:06.880 --> 41:10.070
♫You are my distant call♫

41:08.000 --> 41:09.320
Don't lovers

41:09.340 --> 41:11.250
also need time to themselves?

41:10.770 --> 41:15.040
♫You are my first and last♫

41:11.280 --> 41:12.760
But distance makes the heart colder.

41:13.160 --> 41:13.950
No.

41:13.970 --> 41:14.710
Distance

41:14.880 --> 41:15.770
makes the heart warmer.

41:15.870 --> 41:21.900
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

41:17.750 --> 41:18.460
But I want to...

41:18.480 --> 41:19.040
No.

41:22.220 --> 41:25.180
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

41:22.440 --> 41:23.280
You don't want to.

41:26.390 --> 41:29.980
♫Let's never let go♫

41:30.080 --> 41:31.690
The more you trust me now,

41:31.720 --> 41:32.760
the more you'll want to

41:32.780 --> 41:34.850
tear me up when you recover.

41:34.870 --> 41:36.570
The Demon King is the Demon King after all.

41:36.600 --> 41:38.250
It's better to keep a distance.

41:42.180 --> 41:42.920
Be good.

41:42.940 --> 41:44.030
Sleep alone.

41:46.170 --> 41:46.770
Watch out!

42:16.730 --> 42:18.360
Did the Hua Lin send you here?

42:18.390 --> 42:19.120
Princess.

42:19.140 --> 42:19.820
The Master of Bright Moon

42:19.850 --> 42:21.250
must die here in Outlanders' City.

42:25.500 --> 42:26.620
If you don't want to die,

42:26.850 --> 42:27.520
get lost!

42:27.550 --> 42:28.200
Retreat!

42:38.880 --> 42:40.150
Are we leaving

42:40.170 --> 42:41.300
without completing our order?

42:41.330 --> 42:42.250
General ordered us

42:42.270 --> 42:43.460
not to hurt the Princess.

42:46.060 --> 42:47.510
You took the knife for me.

42:47.530 --> 42:49.330
You could have died, you know?

42:51.370 --> 42:52.410
I'm fine.

42:52.440 --> 42:53.650
I need to protect you.

42:53.670 --> 42:55.020
I remember that.

42:55.910 --> 42:57.710
I just said it casually.

42:57.960 --> 42:59.440
You can't remember anything else,

42:59.460 --> 43:00.900
but you remembered this?

43:00.930 --> 43:02.010
I don't need to remember it.

43:02.740 --> 43:04.000
Because I want to protect you.

43:04.000 --> 43:05.360
Because I want to protect you.

43:13.160 --> 43:15.690
You can't risk your life to protect me.

43:18.020 --> 43:19.940
If something like this happens again,

43:20.020 --> 43:21.230
protect yourself first.

43:21.260 --> 43:22.260
Don't worry about me.

43:24.320 --> 43:25.300
Do you hear me?

43:28.150 --> 43:29.030
I'm asking you.

43:29.050 --> 43:30.010
Do you hear me?

43:37.360 --> 43:38.030
Your hand.

43:39.280 --> 43:40.190
You're feeding him more pills?

43:40.190 --> 43:40.760
What if...

43:45.850 --> 43:47.440
You'll feel sleepy after taking the medicine.

43:47.460 --> 43:48.060
Sleep when you're sleepy.

43:48.090 --> 43:48.990
Don't wait for me.

43:51.450 --> 43:52.840
Tian Huo and I

43:52.860 --> 43:54.100
have something to talk about.

44:05.090 --> 44:06.010
Tian Huo.

44:06.310 --> 44:08.260
I didn't want to ask about your background,

44:08.290 --> 44:10.040
But now monsters are rampant in the city,

44:10.060 --> 44:11.710
Fenlan Banquet is around the corner,

44:11.730 --> 44:13.370
and people just tried to assassinate Fan Yue.

44:13.400 --> 44:14.360
The danger in the city is unpredictable.

44:14.380 --> 44:16.380
We have to find a way to solve this.

44:18.650 --> 44:20.330
I hope you can tell me

44:20.360 --> 44:21.240
everything you know,

44:21.670 --> 44:23.140
including your past.
